<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> als uns ewr gnade
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von
                            <expan>Thoma<ex>n</ex></expan> Kewlers, ewers
                            <expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> zu Folkach, und unsers
                                <expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Trachts <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc.,
                        das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und lassen ewr gnade wissen, daz wir den <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>Hans<ex>en</ex></expan> Tracht <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> czu
                        rede geseczt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Der hat uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t,</expan> daz er dem
                                <expan>obgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>Thoma<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Kewl<ex>er</ex></expan> nichts geczigen hab. Doch
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <add>mit</add> dem
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> so <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
                        gerett, daz er <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> selb <expan>antwurt<ex>en</ex></expan> sol.
                        Denn wo wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
